$ SAS option: syntaxcheck
@ syntaxcheck

`nosyntaxcheck` can be used to prevent entering → Companies-Products/SAS/programming/syntax-check-mode (→ Companies-Products/SAS/what#sas-set-option-obs-0)

{ Enterprise Guide

  → Companies-Products/SAS/Enterprise-Guide[Enterprise Guide] turns syntax checking off at the beginning of every task. So, downstream taks execute normally, *even* after
  errors have occurred!

}

